title: CreditRatingOutlookEnum
description: Represents the enumerated values to specify the credit rating outlook.

oneOf.title: Developing
oneOf.description: Denotes a rating may be raised, lowered, or affirmed.

oneOf.title: Negative
oneOf.description: Denotes a rating may be lowered.

oneOf.title: Positive
oneOf.description: Denotes a rating may be raised.

oneOf.title: Stable
oneOf.description: Denotes a rating is not likely to change.
